s can assign/revoke HR roles for users,\nensuring role-based access control (RBAC).\n• Company management: Approve, edit, and delete company information registered\non the system.\n• Job posting management: Review and manage all job postings from the HR\ndepartment.\n• Candidate management: View candidate lists, track profiles and application\nstatus.\n• Key features:\n• Authentication & Security: Register/log in using JWT authentication, refresh\ntokens, and role-based permissions to protect API endpoints.\n• Smart search: Search and filter jobs by multiple criteria such as industry, location,\nand required skills, helping candidates quickly find suitable jobs.\n\n• Online application: Candidates can upload their CVs in PDF/DOC format directly\nto the system and track their application status.\n• Automatic email: JavaMailSender integration to send an automated confirmation\nemail when a user successfully registers.\n• Smart Cron Job: Schedule recurring emails to notify candidates about new job\npostings that match their skills and industry.	Java\nC++\nPython\nJavaScript\nSpring Boot\nSpring Security\nSpring Data JPA\nHibernate\nMySQL\nMS SQL Server\nReact\nAxios\nReact Router\nJWT\nREST API\nJavaMailSender\nThymeleaf\nSQL\nGit\nGitHub\nVersion Control\nBack-end Development\nObject-Oriented Programming\nDesign Patterns\nWeb Development\nDatabase Management\nSOLID principles\nAuthentication and authorization\nRole-based access control\nCRUD operations\nSearch and filtering\nEmail notification workflows\nApplication tracking	new	2026-05-13 15:48:24.190269+00	2026-05-14 08:16:42.812132+00	cv_pdf	HongNguen.pdf	processed	llm_hybrid	0.95	synced	\N	2026-05-13 15:48:39.136732+00	{"summary": "Backend Java Developer based in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam with career goals focused on applying Java and Spring Boot to real-world backend projects and improving development and teamwork skills.", "technical_skills": [{"name": "Java", "canonical": "java", "source": "llm_structured", "se