17	Senior AI Engineer	Experienced AI Engineer responsible for creating innovative technology solutions focused on Artificial Intelligence, Big Data, IoT, and process automation to support digital transformation initiatives.	Artificial Intelligence\nMachine Learning\nBig Data\nInternet of Things\nProcess Automation\nConvolutional Neural Networks\nRecurrent Neural Networks\nYOLO\nTransformer Models\nBERT\nT5\nData Preprocessing\nNatural Language Processing\nOptical Character Recognition\nImage Analysis\nText Analysis\nModel Optimization\nONNX\nTFLite\nTensorRT\nDatabase Relationships\nACID Transactions\nData Consistency\nCNN\nRNN\nTransformer\nGit\nGitLab\nCI/CD\nDocker\nMLOps\nMLflow\nClearML\nAI/ML Research and Development\nSolution Architecture\nStrategic Roadmapping\nDigital Transformation\nEmerging Technology Evaluation\nPrototype Commercialization\nMicroservices Architecture\nScalable AI Systems\nSoftware Design Patterns\nClean and Reusable Code\nQuality and Reliability Assurance	draft	2026-05-12 16:21:55.510332+00	2026-05-12 16:21:55.518177+00	Architect strategic roadmaps and provide visionary planning.\nDeliver next-generation solutions centered on AI platforms.\nWork with IoT smart automation as an added advantage.\nExplore emerging technology trends and translate insights into competitive advantages.\nCollaborate across departments to turn prototypes into commercial successes.\nEnsure quality, reliability, and creativity in delivered solutions.\nAdvise senior management with progress updates and strategic insights.	Bachelor’s or Master’s degree in Computer Science, Data Science, or a related field.\n5–7+ years of experience in AI/ML R&D.\nHands-on experience with CNN, RNN, YOLO, Transformer, BERT, and T5.\nStrong skills in data preprocessing, NLP, OCR, and image/text analysis.\nProficiency with Git/GitLab, CI/CD, Docker, and MLOps tools including MLflow and ClearML.\nSkill in model optimization using ONNX, TFLite, and TensorRT.\nExperience with microservices architecture for scalable AI systems.\nKnowledge of database relationships, ACID transactions, and data consistency.\nAbility to apply software design patterns for clean, reusable code.	Senior AI Engineer\nJob description\nWe’re looking for an experienced AI Engineer to create innovative technology solutions,\nfocusing on areas such as Artificial Intelligence (AI), Big Data, Internet of Things (IoT), and\nprocess automation. This role requires a blend of deep technical expertise and strategic\nthinking to drive digital transformation initiatives.\nWorking location: 2nd Floor, Anna Building, Quang Trung Software City, District 12, HCMC\nWorking time: Monday to Friday\nWhat You’ll Own & Drive\nArchitect the future with strategic roadmaps and visionary planning\nDeliver next-gen solutions centered on AI platforms; IoT smart automation is an added\nadvantage\nExplore emerging tech trends and translate insights into competitive advantages\nCollaborate across departments to turn prototypes into commercial successes\nEnsure top-tier quality, reliability, and creativity in every solution\nAdvise senior management with clear progress updates and strategic insights\nJob requirement\nBachelor’s or Master’s in Computer Science, Data Science, or related field\n5–7+ years in AI/ML R&D\nHands-on with CNN, RNN, YOLO, Transformer, BERT, T5\nStrong in data preprocessing, NLP, OCR, image/text analysis\nProficient with Git/GitLab, CI/CD, Docker, MLOps (MLflow, ClearML)\nSkilled in model optimization (ONNX, TFLite, TensorRT)\nExperience with Microservices architecture for scalable AI systems\nKnowledge of database relationships, ACID transactions, and data consistency\nAbility to apply software design patterns for clean, reusable code\n1/1	jd_pdf	careerviet.vn-Senior AI Engineer.pdf	processed	{"title": "Senior AI Engineer", "summary": "Experienced AI Engineer responsible for creating innovative technology solutions focused on Artificial Intelligence, Big Data, IoT, and process automati